{"title":"Namp的使用","uid":"53564643197186a30bf1d844fb5f7565","slug":"Namp使用教程","date":"2022-04-14T07:18:15.522Z","updated":"2022-04-15T07:14:13.916Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/Namp使用教程.json","keywords":null,"cover":null,"content":"<h2 id=\"Namp原理\"><a href=\"#Namp原理\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Namp原理\"></a>Namp原理</h2><p>nmap向所在网段发送大量ARP请求广播，如果目标主机存活，则会收到ARP响应，若一段时间后没有收到相应，则认为主机死亡。</p>\n<h2 id=\"Nmap安装\"><a href=\"#Nmap安装\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Nmap安装\"></a>Nmap安装</h2><p>windows系统可去官网自行下载【<a href=\"https://nmap.org/\">下载地址</a>】<br>kali自带namp工具，其他Linux可直接安装：</p>\n<pre class=\"line-numbers language-shell\" data-language=\"shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\">root@kali: # yum install nmap<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n\n\n<h2 id=\"Nmap常用命令\"><a href=\"#Nmap常用命令\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Nmap常用命令\"></a>Nmap常用命令</h2><h4 id=\"活跃主机识别：\"><a href=\"#活跃主机识别：\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"活跃主机识别：\"></a>活跃主机识别：</h4><pre class=\"line-numbers language-shell\" data-language=\"shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\">\nnmap -sP [网段]\n\nnping -tcp -p 445 -data [十六进制数据] [目标ip] #对目标的445端口，以tcp的方式发送一串十六进制的数据\n（可以通过上诉方法进行模拟常见的网络攻击，可以测试对方的防御效果）\n\nnmap -Pn #将所有主机视为在线，跳过主机发现\n\namap -bq [目标ip] [端口] #服务枚举\n\nnmap -sL #简单扫描目标<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n\n<h4 id=\"端口扫描：\"><a href=\"#端口扫描：\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"端口扫描：\"></a>端口扫描：</h4><pre class=\"line-numbers language-shell\" data-language=\"shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\">-sS #隐秘扫描（不形成三次握手），不建立tcp连接，所以不会在防火墙上留下痕迹\n\n-sT #tcp扫描，普通扫描\n\n-sA #使用TCP的ACK进行扫描\n\n-sU #UDP扫描\n\n-sI #使用udp扫描\n\n-sF #FIN扫描\n\n-b&lt;FTP中继主机&gt; #FTP反弹扫描\n\n-p #扫描指定端口<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>\n<h4 id=\"版本侦测\"><a href=\"#版本侦测\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"版本侦测:\"></a>版本侦测:</h4><pre class=\"line-numbers language-shell\" data-language=\"shell\"><code class=\"language-shell\">nmap -sV [目标ip] #服务器指纹识别\n\n–version-intensity #设置版本扫描强度（0-9）\n\n–version-all #尝试每个强度探测\n\n–version-trace #显示详细的版本扫描活动（用于调试）<span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span><span></span></span></code></pre>","text":"Namp原理nmap向所在网段发送大量ARP请求广播，如果目标主机存活，则会收到ARP响应，若一段时间后没有收到相应，则认为主机死亡。 Nmap安装windows系统可去官网自行下载【下载地址】kali自带namp工具，其他Linux可直接安装： root@kali: # yum...","link":"","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":652,"symbolsTime":"1 mins."},"categories":[],"tags":[{"name":"内网渗透工具","slug":"内网渗透工具","count":1,"path":"api/tags/内网渗透工具.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#Namp%E5%8E%9F%E7%90%86\"><span class=\"toc-text\">Namp原理</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#Nmap%E5%AE%89%E8%A3%85\"><span class=\"toc-text\">Nmap安装</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#Nmap%E5%B8%B8%E7%94%A8%E5%91%BD%E4%BB%A4\"><span class=\"toc-text\">Nmap常用命令</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-4\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E6%B4%BB%E8%B7%83%E4%B8%BB%E6%9C%BA%E8%AF%86%E5%88%AB%EF%BC%9A\"><span class=\"toc-text\">活跃主机识别：</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-4\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E7%AB%AF%E5%8F%A3%E6%89%AB%E6%8F%8F%EF%BC%9A\"><span class=\"toc-text\">端口扫描：</span></a></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-4\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E7%89%88%E6%9C%AC%E4%BE%A6%E6%B5%8B\"><span class=\"toc-text\">版本侦测:</span></a></li></ol></li></ol></li></ol>","author":{"name":"DWY","slug":"blog-author","av